{"word":"H6823 - צָפָה - tsâphâh - tsaw-faw' - Cover","slug":"H6823","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צָפָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tsâphâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tsaw-faw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cover"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E6;&#x05E4;&#x05D4; - tsa&#x0302;pha&#x0302;h</b> - <i>tsaw-faw'</i><p/>A primitive root (probably rather identical with <a href=\"#/H6822\">H6822</a> through the idea of <i>expansion</i> in outlook transformed to act); to <i>sheet</i> over (especially with metal): - cover, overlay."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6826\">H6826</a>, <a href=\"#/H6844\">H6844</a>, <a href=\"#/H6858\">H6858</a>"}]}